commitResults.messageTitle: Add further details to the help window
commitResults.messageBody:
The help window currently only links to user guide which is lengthy and may turn off new users from picking up the app.

Adding summarised portions of the user guide would increase the readability

As a step to improving the new user experience, summarised part os the user guide is added to the help window to make learning how to use the app easier

JsonAdaptedTag as per model.person package structure.

commitResults.messageBody:
Previously, the edit command would incorrectly clear the properties of a
seller, just because the edit command didn't contain a pr/ tag, even
though the user's intention could be to edit other details of said
seller.

Other general fix to tidy up the code for a more proper structure &
Separation of Concern, where the EditCommandParser only parses the user
input & EditCommand identifies any inconsistency of pr/ & pf/ tags in
the user input.
